data.description: Welcome home to this beautifully updated 3-bedroom, 2-bath ranch, boasting a super functional floor plan designed for comfortable living. Step inside to discover new LVP flooring, modern granite countertops, and fresh bathroom vanities that set the stage for contemporary elegance. The large updated covered back deck offers a perfect outdoor oasis for relaxation and entertaining, while the convenience of a 1-car garage and a newer roof adds to the appeal. Situated in a prime location offering easy access to Fort Liberty.
